title: Stop storing GeoPoints in memory array.
message:
Stop storing GeoPoints in memory array.

Performance was awful when more than 300 points were in array.
This checkin removes both the GeoPoint and the Overlay arrays
during recording; and creates just the overlay when the map
is viewed.

Still need to improve performance of building the overlay.
